  - Specifically, `Algebra.TensorProduct.assoc R S T U V` is `(T ⊗[S] U) ⊗[R] V ≃ₐ[R] T ⊗[S] (U ⊗[R] V)` when `T` is an `S`-algebra and `U`, `V` are `R`-algebras (but this is getting complicated).
